00:13:24.660 --> 00:13:28.460
wild type and mutant, although they did not speak

230
00:13:28.560 --> 00:13:31.580
about the HIF1 beta mutation, so that's less clear.

231
00:13:33.060 --> 00:13:36.740
Now, for us, this led us to try to develop second generation inhibitors.

232
00:13:37.360 --> 00:13:40.650
And I partnered with a company, Aroha Pharmaceuticals, who developed a first

