962
00:55:47.728 --> 00:55:51.268
Perhaps it's some sort of immune tolerance that makes immunotherapy more

963
00:55:51.308 --> 00:55:54.028
challenging, and also as the

964
00:55:55.608 --> 00:55:59.568
renal cell carcinoma is metastasized, they potentially become

965
00:55:59.608 --> 00:56:03.008
a little bit more HIF-2alpha indifferent than in other

966
00:56:03.068 --> 00:56:07.008
situations. So I think I would treat this individual

967
00:56:07.028 --> 00:56:08.148
with an IO TKI.

968
00:56:09.428 --> 00:56:13.038
You probably would not be able to get belzutifan in the frontline setting because

969
00:56:13.068 --> 00:56:16.548
