970
00:56:16.588 --> 00:56:19.748
TKIs before you actually can get to belzutifan.

971
00:56:19.768 --> 00:56:21.507
So I would probably treat this person with an IO TKI.

972
00:56:21.548 --> 00:56:25.428
Okay. Many thanks. And I'm interested to participate to the database

973
00:56:25.448 --> 00:56:26.968
collection if possible.

974
00:56:27.028 --> 00:56:27.708
Okay. Absolutely.

975
00:56:28.908 --> 00:56:29.488
Thanks, Eric.

976
00:56:30.488 --> 00:56:34.248
So I'm going to bring us home with all the data about HIF inhibition in the

977
00:56:34.288 --> 00:56:37.788
sporadic setting. I don't know if I introduced myself.

