01:03:00.264 --> 01:03:02.564
and still is, a standard of care in this setting.

1091
01:03:02.664 --> 01:03:04.274
Cabo monotherapy, it's just the way--

1092
01:03:05.444 --> 01:03:08.494
where drugs end up is also a function of how drug development proceeds, which is

