1116
01:04:30.384 --> 01:04:34.164
Again, no difference in OS. I think this was a more promising signal than we saw in

1117
01:04:34.284 --> 01:04:37.584
005. You remember that hazard ratio at the final was 0.92.

1118
01:04:37.664 --> 01:04:40.144
This is 0.85 at the initial analysis.

1119
01:04:41.464 --> 01:04:43.904
I'm not remembering the median follow-up. I think it was about two years.

1120
01:04:43.964 --> 01:04:47.644
Looked like minimum follow-up when the censoring starts is about 16 to 18 months.

