01:04:47.684 --> 01:04:50.094
So we'll see how this story plays out.

1122
01:04:50.124 --> 01:04:53.944
Refractory kidney cancer has been a very difficult setting to show an overall

1123
01:04:53.954 --> 01:04:57.554
