1129
01:05:14.964 --> 01:05:17.134
And I think we're seeing additive effects, and I think Eric mentioned this.

1130
01:05:17.184 --> 01:05:19.524
This is not synergy. It's probably sub-additive, actually.

1131
01:05:21.144 --> 01:05:23.744
Response rate, again, we do see some CRs, a small number.

1132
01:05:24.784 --> 01:05:28.344
Remember, with belzu monotherapy, it was 34% primary PD.

1133
01:05:28.424 --> 01:05:32.244
Now it's 5%. So TKIs are really good at controlling tumors and

1134
01:05:32.284 --> 01:05:35.384
