01:07:04.532 --> 01:07:08.032
7% difference, and pembro versus placebo was about the same.

1165
01:07:08.052 --> 01:07:11.892
It was about a 7% or 8% difference at similar time points and follow-up.

1166
01:07:11.952 --> 01:07:14.932
So, another notch of benefit here.

1167
01:07:15.212 --> 01:07:18.302
You see median follow-up over two years. This is early.

1168
01:07:19.032 --> 01:07:22.212
Kidney cancer patients, even high risk, take five to six years to recur on average,

1169
01:07:22.252 --> 01:07:25.992
so this is really early, but obviously these curves split early and stay split,

1170
01:07:26.132 --> 01:07:27.512
until we get up to the censoring.

1171
01:07:29.332 --> 01:07:32.252
But no difference in OS. Again, this hazard ratio is fairly

